{"tid":2394150,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel落實打造《黑豹》影集　故事聚焦瓦干達王國背後故事","createTime":"2021-02-04T03:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T05:21:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39dd74cf09a9942e6b33b50168e7e4fcc593d902","tid":2394150,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"Marvel在2020年未有大片上映，MCU第4階段全部推到2021年才上映，當中由影集《WandaVision》打響頭炮，之後更會有《The Falcon and the Winter Soldier》、《Loki》、《What If...?》等等，近日Marvel更宣布會打造《黑豹》影集，將故事聚焦在瓦干達王國之中。<br />\n<br />\n2020年8月飾演「黑豹」的查特域克保斯曼（Chadwick Boseman）因大腸癌而不幸逝世，終年43歲。現時《黑豹2》定於2022年7月8日上映，前期工作已在進行中，Marvel Studios於去年11月宣布不會為「黑豹」空缺而進行重新選角，同時亦不會以「電腦合成」（CGI）的形式將國王T'Challa呈現在戲中，加上會由誰來接任國王一位同樣未知。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指出《黑豹》的導演Ryan Coogler將會繼續執導《黑豹》2及《黑豹》影集，《黑豹》當初全球獲得大成功，在奧斯卡上更獲得「最佳原創音樂獎」、「最佳服裝設計獎」以及「最佳藝術指導獎」三項大獎，更曾入圍競爭最佳電影，成為Marvel首套獲得奧斯卡獎項的電影。<br />\n<br />\n當時瓦干達王國雖有在《黑豹》中出現，影迷看到戲中的瓦干達王國無一不讚做工仔細、宏偉、美麗、不同的部落加上他們擁有的高科技，簡直令人眼前一亮，它更是《復仇者聯盟 3：無限之戰》的最後戰場，相信在瓦干達王國之中，還能發展出更多不同的故事，在影集中應該會看得到更深入、不同面貌的瓦干達，令人十分期待。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201113/403904470292893696970164.jpeg/Rt8b3BzZAYXiHyYNNgRO4hiBJFVr9tnoyGK3TMhit0w?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201113%2F403904470292893696970164.jpeg%2FRt8b3BzZAYXiHyYNNgRO4hiBJFVr9tnoyGK3TMhit0w%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b44aaf49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abbd845f6e5ecab463f3b30cb9202aa731c80054","tid":2394150,"uid":207012,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"打你老母造呀"},{"pid":"3a211c72bdf481ee8b645b0630e491032e810d3e","tid":2394150,"uid":49151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acjPqOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacjPqOt.jpg&h=7d348840&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac83aea7d1d0ed402772133e845b23574f4df88","tid":2394150,"uid":249940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a211c72bdf481ee8b645b0630e491032e810d3e","tid":2394150,"uid":49151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acjPqOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacjPqOt.jpg&h=7d348840&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"關咩事"},{"pid":"213d77e243d78dfb6c8fd04cf1f4cfead5b86fbf","tid":2394150,"uid":49151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bac83aea7d1d0ed402772133e845b23574f4df88","tid":2394150,"uid":249940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a211c72bdf481ee8b645b0630e491032e810d3e","tid":2394150,"uid":49151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acjPqOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacjPqOt.jpg&h=7d348840&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"關咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"又係你隻m狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d280c7b638c39d332986c78a912d2893966661b2","tid":2394150,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"喂你班左膠唔係話角色同膚色係無關係嫁咩<br />\n做咩唔搵個亞洲人扮黑豹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}